<script type="text/javascript">
var isMobile = false;
// Ready:
$(function () {
checkCookieConsent();
bindNavLinks();
bindLogout();
bindSocialMediaLinks();
friendlyDates();
// Enable Twitter plugin, can toggle to false
// based on other conditions.
csTwitter.init(true);
});
// Checks whether the current user has accepted the cookie policy popup,
// shows banner notification when cookie is not present.
function checkCookieConsent() {
// Consent cookie:
var consentCookie = "hdidCookieConsentDismissed";
var consentDismissed = csUtilities.getCookie(consentCookie); // returns true/false.
if (consentDismissed === "undefined" || !consentDismissed) {
bootler.prompt({
type: "info",
containerType: "topPush",
textAlign: "center",
msg: "This website uses cookies. " +
"By continuing to use this website you are giving consent to cookies being used. " +
"<a href='/Home/CookiePolicy' target='_blank'>Read more</a>",
onDismiss: function () {
csUtilities.setGlobalCookie(consentCookie, "true", 365);
}
});
}
}
// UI Bind: buttons on nav that are exceptional:
function bindNavLinks() {
// For classic hdid:
$(document).on("click", "#nav-btn-o-hdid", function (e) {
e.preventDefault();
mootler.okCancel({
modalTitle: "<i class='fa fa-clock-o'></i> Leaving so Soon?",
modalMessage: $("#modal-old-hdid-modal").html(),
confirmButtonName: "Return to classic HowDidiDo",
onConfirm: function () {
window.open("http://classic.howdidido.com/", "_blank");
}
});
});
// For contact link:
$(document).on("click", "#nav-btn-contact", function (e) {
e.preventDefault();
mootler.ok({
modalTitle: "<i class='fa fa-envelope-o'></i> Contact Us",
modalMessage: $("#modal-beta-contact-modal").html()
});
});
}
// UI Bind: what the log out button does:
function bindLogout() {
$(document).on("click", "#btn-logout", function (e) {
e.preventDefault();
$("form#logoutForm").submit();
});
}
// UI Bind: Social media links.
function bindSocialMediaLinks() {
// Enable facebook share.
$(document).on("click", ".cs-fb-share-dlg", function (e) {
ga('send', 'event', 'Timeline', 'Share', 'Facebook'); // Record scroll with analytics
e.preventDefault();
csFacebook.shareWithDialog({
itemId: $(this).attr("data-event-id"),
date: $(this).attr("data-event-date"),
preview: $(this).attr("data-event-preview")
});
});
// Enable Twitter tweet.
$(document).on("click", ".cs-tw-tweet", function (e) {
ga('send', 'event', 'Timeline', 'Share', 'Twitter'); // Record scroll with analytics
e.preventDefault();
csTwitter.tweet({
itemId: $(this).attr("data-event-id"),
date: $(this).attr("data-event-date"),
preview: $(this).attr("data-event-preview")
});
});
$(document).on("click", ".cs-tw-tweet-text-oom", function (e) {
e.preventDefault();
csTwitter.tweetOOMInvite();
});
$(document).on("click", ".cs-tw-tweet-text-pcuk", function (e) {
e.preventDefault();
csTwitter.tweetPCUKInvite();
});
// Enable email share..
$(document).on("click", ".cs-email-share", function (e) {
ga('send', 'event', 'Timeline', 'Share', 'Email'); // Record scroll with analytics
e.preventDefault();
csUtilities.SendEventToEmailClient({
itemId: $(this).attr("data-event-id"),
date: $(this).attr("data-event-date"),
user: $(this).attr("data-event-sender")
});
});
}
</script>

var filterStatsData = function() {
filter = "";
//Build the list of selected courses
$('.filter ul li.selected').each(function() {
var self = $(this);
filter = filter + self.html().trim().toLowerCase() + '|';
});
//filter the data
//by courses
if (filter == 'all|') {
currentData = allData;
} else {
currentData = new jinqJs()
.from(allData)
.where(function(row) { return (filter.indexOf(row.CourseDesc.toLowerCase() + "|") > -1); }).select();
}
//by date
currentData = new jinqJs()
.from(currentData)
.where(function(row) { return (moment(row.Date).isAfter(filterDate)); }).select();
}
// On Ready:
$(function() {
// Setting filters:
setFilterKeys(["broomieknowe 18 white card","white tees 2014","white tees 2011","yellow tees 2011","white tees"]);
$('.filter > ul li:not(.disabled)').on("click",
function() {
filterStatsData();
updateOverview();
updateStats();
updateCharts();
}
);
$('input[name="optTime"]').click(function(e) {
var timeRange = $('input[name="optTime"]:checked').val();
if (timeRange == "year") {
filterDate = moment().year() + '/01/01';
} else {
filterDate = '1990/01/01';
}
filterStatsData();
updateOverview();
updateStats();
updateCharts();
});
$('.collapse').on('show.bs.collapse', function() {
$(this).prev().addClass('highlight');
$(this).addClass('highlight');
});
$('.collapse').on('hidden.bs.collapse', function() {
$(this).prev().removeClass('highlight');
$(this).removeClass('highlight');
});
//dropdowns for holebyhole round information

var hole1 = $(this).find("[data-putts-hole='1']");
var putts = hole1.val();
if (putts == "0") {
hole1.click().focus().select();
}
}, 500);
});
});
// Update Stats:
var updateStats = function() {
var bestIn = 0;
var bestOut = 0;
var bestTotal = 0;
var avgIn = 0;
var avgOut = 0;
var avgTotal = 0;
for (var i = 1; i < 19; i++) {
var idx = holeToIdx(i);
var avg = avgScore(i);
var bst = bestScore(i);
var par = holePar(i);
bestTotal += bst;
avgTotal += parseFloat(avg);
if (i < 10) {
bestOut += bst;
avgOut += parseFloat(avg);
} else {
bestIn += bst;
avgIn += parseFloat(avg);
}
$(".statistics-summary .average ul li:nth-child(" + idx + ")").text(avg);
var b = $(".statistics-summary .best ul li:nth-child(" + idx + ")");
b.text(bst);
b.removeClass("par").removeClass("birdie").removeClass("bogey").removeClass("better").removeClass("worse");
if (par > 0) {
//set the correct hole colour
switch ((par - bst)) {
case 0:
b.addClass("par");
break;
case 1:
b.addClass("birdie");
break;
case -1:
b.addClass("bogey");
break;
default:
if ((par - bst) >= 2) {
b.addClass("better");
}
if ((par - bst) <= -2) {
b.addClass("worse");
}
break;
}
}
}
$(".statistics-summary .average ul li:nth-child(24)").text(avgTotal.toFixed(1));
$(".statistics-summary .best ul li:nth-child(24)").text(bestTotal);
$(".statistics-summary .average ul li:nth-child(12)").text(avgOut.toFixed(1));
$(".statistics-summary .best ul li:nth-child(12)").text(bestOut);
$(".statistics-summary .average ul li:nth-child(23)").text(avgIn.toFixed(1));
$(".statistics-summary .best ul li:nth-child(23)").text(bestIn);
}
// Helper - Average Score:
var avgScore = function(holeNo) {
var total = 0;
var played = 0;
var holes = $(".statistics-history ul.result li:nth-child(" + holeToIdx(holeNo) + "):visible");
holes.each(function(idx) {
var score = parseInt($(this).text())
if(score > 0)
played ++;
total += score;
});
return (total / played).toFixed(1);
}
// Helper - Hole Par:
var holePar = function(holeNo) {
var par = -1;
var holes = $(".statistics-history ul.result li:nth-child(" + holeToIdx(holeNo) + "):visible");
holes.each(function(idx) {
var hp = parseInt($(this).attr("data-hole-par"));
if (par === -1) par = hp;
if (hp !== 0 && par !== hp) {
par = 0;
return false;
}
});
return par;
}
// Helper - Best Score:
var bestScore = function(holeNo) {
var best = 99;
var holes = $(".statistics-history ul.result li:nth-child(" + holeToIdx(holeNo) + "):visible");
holes.each(function(idx) {
var g = parseInt($(this).text());
if (best > g && g !== 0) {
best = g;
}
});
return (best === 99 ? 0 : best);
}
// Helper - Worst Score:
var worstScore = function(holeNo) {
var worst = 0;
var holes = $(".statistics-history ul.result li:nth-child(" + holeToIdx(holeNo) + "):visible");
holes.each(function() {
var g = parseInt($(this).text());
if (worst < g && g != 0) {
worst = g;
}
});
return (worst === 99 ? 0 : worst);
}
// Helper - Hole to Idx:
var holeToIdx = function(holeNo) {
var idx = holeNo < 10 ? 2 : 4;
return idx + holeNo;
}
// Update Overiew:
var updateOverview = function() {
if (currentData == null) {
$('.stats-available').hide();
$('.no-stats-available').show();
return;
}
//Summaries
var holesInOne = new jinqJs().from(currentData).sum('HolesInOne').select();
var eaglesBetter = new jinqJs().from(currentData).sum('EaglesBetter').select();
var birdies = new jinqJs().from(currentData).sum('Birdies').select();
var pars = new jinqJs().from(currentData).sum('Pars').select();
var bogeys = new jinqJs().from(currentData).sum('Bogeys').select();
var doubleBogeys = new jinqJs().from(currentData).sum('DoubleBogeys').select();
var qualifiers = new jinqJs().from(currentData).sum('Qualifier').select();
var holesEmbelleished = new jinqJs().from(currentData).sum('Holes').select();
var gir = new jinqJs().from(currentData).sum('GreensInReg').select();
var putts = new jinqJs().from(currentData).sum('Putts').select();
$('#Rounds').html(currentData.length);
$('#Distance').html(Math.floor((currentData.length * courseDisance) / 1760));
$('.stats-available').toggle(currentData.length > 0);
$('.no-stats-available').toggle(currentData.length === 0);
$('#HolesInOne').html(holesInOne);
//total height
var total = parseInt(eaglesBetter) + parseInt(birdies) + parseInt(pars) + parseInt(bogeys) + parseInt(doubleBogeys);
$('#EaglesBetter').html(eaglesBetter);
$('#EaglesBetterBar').animate({ width: (Math.max(eaglesBetter, 1) / total) * 100 }, animationTime);
$('#Birdies').html(birdies);
$('#BirdiesBar').animate({ width: (Math.max(birdies, 1) / total) * 100 }, animationTime);
$('#Pars').html(pars);
$('#ParsBar').animate({ width: (Math.max(pars, 1) / total) * 100 }, animationTime);
$('#Bogeys').html(bogeys);
$('#BogeysBar').animate({ width: (Math.max(bogeys, 1) / total) * 100 }, animationTime);
$('#DoubleBogeys').html(doubleBogeys);
$('#DoubleBogeysBar').animate({ width: (Math.max(doubleBogeys, 1) / total) * 100 }, animationTime);
//Hole analysis
parStats = [{ total: 0, played: 0, gotpar: 0 }, { total: 0, played: 0, gotpar: 0 }, { total: 0, played: 0, gotpar: 0 }];
bestResult = 999;
bestComp = 0;
bestSection = 0;
bestDiv = 1;
var holesForGreensInReg = 0;
var bestGross = 999;
var worstGross = 0;
var bestSPoints = 0;
var worstSPoints = 999;
distrbutionData = new Array(3);
for (var i = 0; i < distrbutionData.length; i++) {
distrbutionData[i] = new Array(0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
}
holeData = new Array(18);
for (var i = 0; i < holeData.length; i++) {
holeData[i] = { totalOverPar: 0, played: 0, holeNo: i + 1, best: 99, worst: 0, par: 0, total: 0, avg: 0 };
}
grossScoresData = [];
handicapData = [];
currentData.forEach(function(round) {
if (bestResult > round.Order && round.Order != 0) {
bestResult = round.Order;
bestComp = round.CompNumber;
bestDiv = round.Division;
bestSection = round.SectionId;
}
//Strokeplay / Medal
if (round.CompetitionType === 4 && round.RoundHoleDetailSummaries.length === 18 && round.TotalGross > 0) {
//if (round.CompetitionType === 4) {
//Check for any NR's
var isNR = new jinqJs().from(round.RoundHoleDetailSummaries).sum('NR').select();
if (isNR == 0){
if (bestGross > round.TotalGross) {
bestGross = round.TotalGross;
}
if (worstGross < round.TotalGross) {
worstGross = round.TotalGross;
}
var point = { x: new Object(), y: 0 };
point.x = moment(round.Date).format("LL");;
point.y = round.TotalGross;
grossScoresData.push(point);
}
} else if (round.CompetitionType === 3) {
var points = findScore(round.Score);
if (bestSPoints < points) {
bestSPoints = points;
}
if (worstSPoints > points) {
worstSPoints = points;
}
console.log(round.CompetitionType + ',' + findScore(round.Score));
}
if (round.ExactHandicap != "") {
var hcpPoint = { x: new Object(), y: 0 };
hcpPoint.x = moment(round.Date).format("LL");
hcpPoint.y = parseFloat(round.ExactHandicap);
handicapData.push(hcpPoint);
}
round.RoundHoleDetailSummaries.forEach(function(hole) {
if (hole.NR) return true;
var gross = hole.G;
if (gross === 0) return true;
var par = hole.P;
if (par < 3) return true;
if (par > 5) return true;
parStats[par - 3].total += gross;
parStats[par - 3].played += 1;
holeData[hole.H - 1].total += gross;
holeData[hole.H - 1].totalOverPar += (gross - par);
holeData[hole.H - 1].played += 1;
holeData[hole.H - 1].par = par;
if (holeData[hole.H - 1].best > gross && gross != 0) {
holeData[hole.H - 1].best = gross;
}
if (holeData[hole.H - 1].worst < gross && gross != 0) {
holeData[hole.H - 1].worst = gross;
}
if (gross <= par) parStats[par - 3].gotpar += 1;
if ((gross - par) + 2 < 5) {
distrbutionData[par - 3][(gross - par) + 2] += 1;
} else {
distrbutionData[par - 3][5] += 1;
}
return true;
});
});
//Hole averages
for (var i = 0; i < holeData.length; i++) {
holeData[i].avg = (holeData[i].total / holeData[i].played).toFixed(1);
}
//Best and worst stats
var holeDataSorted = holeData.sort(SortByAvgOverPar);
var bestHole = holeDataSorted[0];
var worstHole = holeDataSorted[holeDataSorted.length - 1];
$('#bestHole .odometer').html(bestHole.holeNo);

var par5Avg = parStats[2].total / Math.max(parStats[2].played, 1);
var par3Per = numberFixer(parStats[0].gotpar, parStats[0].played);
var par4Per = numberFixer(parStats[1].gotpar, parStats[1].played);
var par5Per = numberFixer(parStats[2].gotpar, parStats[2].played);
$('#par3Avg').html(par3Avg.toFixed(1));
$('#par3Avg').closest('.stat').parent().toggle((parStats[0].played > 0));
$('#par4Avg').html(par4Avg.toFixed(1));
$('#par4Avg').closest('.stat').parent().toggle((parStats[1].played > 0));
$('#par5Avg').html(par5Avg.toFixed(1));
$('#par5Avg').closest('.stat').parent().toggle((parStats[2].played > 0));
$('#par3Per').html(par3Per.toFixed(0));
$('#par3Per').closest('.stat').parent().toggle((parStats[0].played > 0));
$('#par4Per').html(par4Per.toFixed(0));
$('#par4Per').closest('.stat').parent().toggle((parStats[1].played > 0));
$('#par5Per').html(par5Per.toFixed(0));
$('#par5Per').closest('.stat').parent().toggle((parStats[2].played > 0));
$('#Qualifiers').html(qualifiers);
setPieChart('#par3PerPie', par3Per);
setPieChart('#par4PerPie', par4Per);
setPieChart('#par5PerPie', par5Per);
$('#GIR').html(((gir / holesEmbelleished) * 100).toFixed(1));
$('#Putts').html((putts / holesEmbelleished).toFixed(1));
}

// Helper - number fixer (?)
var numberFixer = function(num, total) {
var result = ((num / Math.max(total, 1)) * 100);
return result;
}
// Set Pie Chart:
var setPieChart = function(id, value) {
var pie = document.querySelector(id + ' .pie');
var result = value.toFixed(0) + ', 100';
pie.style.strokeDasharray = result;
}
// Show Best Result (redirect):
var ShowBestResult = function() {
window.location = "/My/Result?sectionId=" + bestSection + "&compNumber=" + bestComp + "&division=" + bestDiv;
}
// Returns the literal of integer place:
var place = function(num) {
var orderStr = num.toString();
if (orderStr.endsWith("11") || orderStr.endsWith("12") || orderStr.endsWith("13")) return "th";
if (orderStr.endsWith("1")) return "st";
if (orderStr.endsWith("2")) return "nd";
if (orderStr.endsWith("3")) return "rd";
return "th";
}
// Helper - Find Score:
var findScore = function(result) {
result = (result == null ? "0" : result);
if (result.lastIndexOf(" ") > 0) {
result = result.substring(result.lastIndexOf(" ") + 1,
result.Length - result.lastIndexOf(" ") - 1);
}
return parseInt(result.replace("DQ", "0").replace("NR", "0").replace("N/R", "0").replace("c", "").replace("i", ""));
}
// Helper - Sort by Average Over Par:
function SortByAvgOverPar(a, b) {
var aVal = a.totalOverPar / a.played;
var bVal = b.totalOverPar / b.played;
return ((aVal < bVal) ? -1 : ((aVal > bVal) ? 1 : 0));
}
